			<div class="content" id="post-content-2811741">
									

<p>Finally! Here's the IJAMEA hub, a collaborative project between MrWrong and myself over the last few weeks. This piece is littered with all sorts of history, and one of my favorite aspects is our many nods to entities and concepts created over on the Japanese branch of the wiki. Hope you like it.</p>
