			<div class="content" id="post-content-3812304">
									

<p>The soldiers in the <a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/ijamea-hub/Occultists.jpg">picture</a> are obviously white people instead of Japanese. Besides, all the &quot;occultists&quot; have a &quot;pigtail&quot;, which is forbidden after the Revolution of 1911 in China.</p>
